products.title: ADATA SU800 256GB M.2 2280 SATA 3D NAND Internal SSD (ASU800NS38-256GT-C)
features: SLC Caching to boost read/write performance
Advanced LDPC ECC Engine to reduce in data errors and an increase in data integrity Proprietary Software - Downloadable SSD Toolbox and Migration Utility
Read/Write up to 560/520 MB/s *Performance vary by ssd model.
This SSD uses M andB key. Please check your system spec before purchase.
products.description: Utilizing 3D NAND Flash and a high speed SMI controller, the compact Ultimate SU800 M.2 2280 solid state drive provides capacities up to 1TB and greatly enhances performance, efficiency, and reliability over traditional 2D NAND. It also comes with intelligent SLC Caching and a DRAM Cache to boost read/write performance. Featuring LDPC ECC, high TBW (total bytes written), and DEVSLP (Device Sleep), the SU800 M.2 2280 instantly upgrades notebook and desktop PCs with superior stability, durability, and power efficiency.
